description:
Flyysoulja and Kodiyakredd AKA the "Island Boys" join the podcast to talk about going viral for their pool freestyle and drop a freestyle live on air. We talk about Addison Rae getting banned from TikTok, Megan Fox and MGK's relationship, and the new 'Bones Day' trend. The Island Boys discuss what celebrities would be considered to become island boys.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
